“Cookies” are small text files that may be placed on your Web browser when you visit the Websites or when you view advertisements placed on other websites by Bellecapital AG, Bellecapital International AG or Bellecapital UK Ltd. The information derived from cookies is used for administrative purposes to help Bellecapital AG, Bellecapital International AG and Bellecapital UK Ltd. gauge the effectiveness of its advertising efforts and to improve your experience with the Websites. For example, this information may help authenticate you (i.e., verify that you are who you say you are). Cookies also make it easier for you to navigate the Websites by, among other things, “remembering” your identity so that you do not have to input your password multiple times as you move between pages or services. Cookies also may be used to serve you advertisements when you visit websites of third parties with whom Bellecapital AG, Bellecapital International AG and Bellecapital UK Ltd. may have marketing relationships. You can set your Web browser to inform you when cookies are set, or to prevent cookies from being set. However, if you decline to use cookies, you may experience reduced functionality. The Websites use cookies that last indefinitely. If you do not wish to have a cookie stored in your computer, you should disable them in your browser’s security options.
“Clickstream” data (e.g., information regarding which of our web pages you access, the frequency of such access, and your product and service preferences) may be collected by Bellecapital AG, Bellecapital International AG or Bellecapital UK Ltd. itself, or by its service providers, using cookies, Web beacons, page tags, or similar tools that are set when you visit the Websites or when you view an advertisement that Bellecapital AG, Bellecapital International AG or Bellecapital UK Ltd. has placed on another website. Clickstream data and similar information may be shared internally within Bellecapital AG, Bellecapital International AG and Bellecapital UK Ltd. and used: for administrative purposes; to assess the usage, value and performance of online products and services; to improve your experience with the Websites; and as otherwise permitted by applicable law or regulation. This information may be processed by Bellecapital AG, Bellecapital International AG and Bellecapital UK Ltd. for the purposes described above, or by third parties on behalf of Bellecapital AG, Bellecapital International AG and Bellecapital UK Ltd. When you visit the Websites, your browser may be momentarily directed to the website of an ad server or other third party service provider. This re-direction process will not be apparent to you. These third party websites automatically receive your IP address when this happens, and they may also collect information from your interaction with the Websites including computer and connection information, standard web log information, and ad information. Such information generally does not identify you individually.
Bellecapital AG, Bellecapital International AG and Bellecapital UK Ltd. may make available on its Websites third party applications such as content linking or sharing facilities. Information collected by providers of such applications is governed by their privacy policies. Following links to any other off-site pages or other web sites is at the user's own risk.
This policy provides a general statement of the ways in which Bellecapital AG, Bellecapital International AG and Bellecapital UK Ltd. gather information from the use of its Websites. In connection with specific products or services offered by Bellecapital AG, Bellecapital International AG or Bellecapital UK Ltd., you may be provided with separate privacy policies or statements. This policy may be changed from time to time without notice by Bellecapital AG, Bellecapital International AG and Bellecapital UK Ltd. The revised policy will be effective immediately upon posting to the Websites. This version of the policy is effective April 30, 2015. If you require further information regarding this privacy policy please contact us.

















