Zurich, V8, based Investment company Bellecapital International Ltd. buys PRA Health Sciences Inc, WisdomTree Japan Hedged Equity Fund, SPDR S&P International SmallCap, JD.com Inc, Baidu Inc, iShares MSCI United Kingdom, WisdomTree Europe Hedged Equity Fund, sells Procter & Gamble Co, Cisco Systems Inc, Pfizer Inc, iShares Russell 2000, McKesson Corp during the 3-months ended 2017-06-30, according to the most recent filings of the investment company, Bellecapital International Ltd.. As of 2017-06-30, Bellecapital International Ltd. owns 69 stocks with a total value of $113 million.  These are the details of the buys and sells.New Purchases: PRAH, EWU, HEDJ, Added Positions: DXJ, GWX, JD, BABA, BIDU, WFC, T, AMZN, IBM, BCS, Reduced Positions: PG, CSCO, IBB, SPY, FXI, COO, AAPL, CVS, SLB, GOOGL, Sold Out: PFE, IWM, MCK, CAT, TM, MOSY, HBAN, 
