How do I update this listing?




                                             Bellecapital International Ltd. is based out of Zurich. Bellecapital International Ltd. is a large advisory firm with  More than 100 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $463,000,000 (Form ADV from 2017-03-23).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q2 2017 included $114,105,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 48.81%. Bellecapital International Ltd.'s largest holding is Alibaba Group Holding Limited with shares held of 46,595.  Bellecapital International Ltd. has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 16 13F filings in our database for Bellecapital International Ltd.. 
                                           






